<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/7809640-ricardo">Ricardo</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I have never read &quot;Eva Luna&quot; and I loved all the stories. As far as I know there are some characters that come from the novel but the stories are comp<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I have never read "Eva Luna" and I loved all the stories. As far as I know there are some characters that come from the novel but the stories are completely independent so I guess they can be read on any order. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
