<div id="review_4090249232" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4090249232" />
    <a title="Janet Fu" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/129954563-janet-fu"><img alt="Janet Fu" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4090249232?book_show_action=true">Jul 07, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Janet Fu" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Janet Fu" href="/user/show/129954563-janet-fu">Janet Fu</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4090249232" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1815514968744295600">For an hour I was transported to an exotic humid world full of color, emotion, love, drama, deceit, and passion. The stories are unique in themselves but all of them have the same ambiance - they conjure the same feelings as a heavily perfumed candle atop a braided rug in a dark room. Definitely some of the stories are more enjoyable to read and Allende proves that she has a flair for description </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

